Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.67,0:22:43.21,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}この身を委ねる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.84,0:22:46.67,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}握り締めた冷たい指
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.67,0:22:49.55,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}君は悲しく笑い
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.55,0:22:52.51,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}僕はかける言葉もなく
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.72,0:22:55.47,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}景色は滲む
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.64,0:22:58.44,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}始まればいずれ終わる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.44,0:23:01.35,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}綺麗事などいらない
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.35,0:23:04.40,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}せめて君を温めたい
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.57,0:23:14.41,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}ほんの少しの時間を与えて　神様
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.77,0:22:26.32,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}晨曦的光芒太過耀眼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.78,0:22:32.28,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}令人不禁想要放棄
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.62,0:22:38.33,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}坦露自己的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.67,0:22:43.21,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}任憑此身沉浮
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.84,0:22:46.67,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}你握緊冰冷的十指
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.67,0:22:49.55,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}臉上是悲切的笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.55,0:22:52.51,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}我無言以對
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.72,0:22:55.47,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}只有視野漸漸模糊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.64,0:22:58.44,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}不需言語粉飾
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.44,0:23:01.35,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}有始必定有終
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.35,0:23:04.40,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}唯願能將你溫暖
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.57,0:23:14.41,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}神啊 請給我一點時間
Comment: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,staff1,NTP,0,0,0,,==========STORY==========
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.68,0:00:05.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你應該能救她的！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.67,0:00:07.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是開著法芙娜嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.26,0:00:09.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是你的話…！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.64,0:00:21.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這要是實戰早就進棺材了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.35,0:00:23.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們還是有點潛力的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.13,0:00:23.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.69,0:00:25.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還真是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.79,0:00:29.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是在北面350公里處發現的島嶼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.32,0:00:30.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,確實是挺像的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.20,0:00:34.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,樂園計畫下建造的島嶼並不只有Alvis
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.46,0:00:39.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即便是為了弄清這一點 我也認為值得去走一趟
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.59,0:00:47.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,連真矢你也被派出來了嗎 也是辛苦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.86,0:00:52.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一騎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.86,0:00:56.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過是清掃了翔子的墓
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.24,0:01:01.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就以為算是贖過罪了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.45,0:01:03.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一騎！
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,（OP）
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.75,0:03:14.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡應該也有過很多人的回憶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.00,0:03:15.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.35,0:03:19.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,趁著還沒受傷趕緊下來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.92,0:03:21.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.86,0:03:38.40,title1,NTP,0,0,200,,{\fad(500,500)}第８回
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.48,0:03:38.40,title2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur35\t(0,600,\blur0)\fad(0,500)}固　　　　執
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.57,0:03:38.40,title3,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(720,1000)\fad(300,500)}甲 洋
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.73,0:03:38.40,loc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}龍宮島坐標：南緯08°59′18〞 東經172°25′53〞
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.29,0:03:54.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,甲洋 我們也往一點鐘方向移動
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.10,0:03:58.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你沒資格命令我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.52,0:03:59.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別抬槓 甲洋
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.26,0:04:01.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在可是在作戰行動中
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.86,0:04:02.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作戰行動麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.59,0:04:08.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就是用這個藉口拋棄翔子的嗎 總士
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.99,0:04:15.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,甲洋 總士肯定不會…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.89,0:04:30.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看樣子進展挺順利的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.63,0:04:33.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,估計傍晚之前可以完成
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.76,0:04:34.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和計畫的一樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.63,0:04:37.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,分隊的情況怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.77,0:04:39.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正在行動
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.09,0:04:46.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,彙報一下情況
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.17,0:04:51.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事事如意果然不可能啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.25,0:04:56.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個…這件事溝口先生不知道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.30,0:04:58.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當然
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.53,0:05:08.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用理會他
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.46,0:05:39.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這些區域都很老舊了 小心點啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.91,0:05:41.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼情況
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.90,0:05:49.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.18,0:05:53.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快叫醫療班來！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.88,0:05:56.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,地下區域發生意外 有一人受傷
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.82,0:05:58.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,分隊那邊也來消息了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.32,0:06:00.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說是發現入口了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.78,0:06:08.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的不用報告溝口先生嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.59,0:06:10.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正他也不會懂得我們的想法的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.20,0:06:12.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,畢竟是個老頑固
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.44,0:06:21.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,溝口先生 剛才的聲音是…？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.91,0:06:23.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遠見
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.84,0:06:28.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人手不夠 你也一起來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.53,0:06:30.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.87,0:06:33.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 幹活去幹活去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.30,0:06:35.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我倒想問溝口先生你有沒有幹勁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.14,0:06:38.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幹勁都被年輕人吸光啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.27,0:06:39.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抓緊一點
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.82,0:06:52.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 我也幹活去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.73,0:07:05.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思 能換個人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.53,0:07:07.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了 不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.75,0:07:17.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,發現目標
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.93,0:07:20.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,照計畫行事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.37,0:07:27.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,系統還在運作啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.29,0:07:50.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,登陸部隊的溝口先生來電
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.56,0:07:53.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接到我的專線來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.50,0:07:54.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.78,0:07:58.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你那邊情況怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.48,0:08:03.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老師好像準備在島上尋寶啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.77,0:08:07.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是給我發現了 能隨便我處理嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.75,0:08:11.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那要在你搞清楚他們打算怎麼處置寶貝之後
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.68,0:08:13.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.98,0:08:47.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在那裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.20,0:09:02.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.15,0:09:07.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要讀取我的心…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.44,0:09:13.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.80,0:09:26.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.01,0:09:31.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們就是被招來的另一個Alvis嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.93,0:09:33.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.09,0:09:35.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 發生什麼事了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.92,0:09:36.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快報告
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.62,0:09:39.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡的內核已經不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.43,0:09:43.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.07,0:09:45.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.08,0:09:47.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是你
