Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.35,0:10:14.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出現位置在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.81,0:10:16.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,北面350公里處
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.47,0:10:18.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,登陸部隊正執行作戰行動的島嶼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.12,0:10:21.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼原因導致的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.68,0:10:22.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.70,0:10:27.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,馬上脫離
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.44,0:10:43.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敵人出現了 工作人員有危險
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.59,0:10:44.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.78,0:10:46.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼就不能早點知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.29,0:10:49.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,馬上讓登陸部隊撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.16,0:10:59.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}確保撤離路線 同時抓緊彙報傷亡情況
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.05,0:10:59.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弓子 真矢呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.98,0:11:02.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別慌 媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.76,0:11:14.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請求救援！喂 有在聽嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.60,0:11:16.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,撤退情況怎麼樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.03,0:11:20.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,工作人員和醫療班還在地下設施裡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.02,0:11:23.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,優先進行運輸機的起飛準備
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.92,0:11:25.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你打算拋下他們嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.92,0:11:27.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老師
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.12,0:11:34.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇 好恐怖
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.57,0:11:35.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好凶好凶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.35,0:11:52.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就是去救他們也只會白忙活
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.66,0:11:54.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以說沒經驗的人就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.22,0:11:58.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,保護小孩也是大人的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.73,0:12:15.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,準備好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.88,0:12:17.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,囉囉嗦嗦的煩不煩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.43,0:12:18.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,趕緊讓我出擊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.72,0:12:21.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,LDA展開
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.72,0:12:23.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第1、第2固定栓 鎖定
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.61,0:12:25.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第3、第4固定栓 鎖定
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.06,0:12:27.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,法芙娜 移出機架
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.58,0:12:29.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,AVC飛龍 運至轉盤
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.22,0:12:31.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,移動至轉乘區
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.26,0:12:41.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最終安全裝置檢查 全部正常
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.18,0:12:42.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,法芙娜 已固定於連接位置
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.85,0:12:44.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,連接臂 鎖定
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.08,0:13:03.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.59,0:13:15.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我絕對不會拋棄同伴的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.20,0:13:17.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,絕對不會！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.10,0:13:31.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在那裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.72,0:13:36.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,救命 救…啊——
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.70,0:13:42.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,分隊好像全軍覆沒了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.42,0:13:49.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是說 沒必要繼續留在島上了啊
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,(Part-b)
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.07,0:14:04.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經確認到這個島上也有芬里爾
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.48,0:14:08.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,應該立即引爆 炸毀這個島
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.33,0:14:12.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在猶豫什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.30,0:14:16.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是一舉殲滅敵人的機會
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.84,0:14:19.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都不等撤退完成麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.78,0:14:23.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我倒認為這比友軍被對方同化成為敵人要好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.59,0:14:27.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請批准使用芬里爾
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.37,0:14:30.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了 我批准
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.56,0:14:33.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真壁…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.20,0:14:37.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總士
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.74,0:14:40.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有件事希望你去做
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.04,0:15:01.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 這就拉你上來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.19,0:15:05.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事的 我可以自己…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.00,0:15:17.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在那裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.21,0:15:43.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,命挺大啊 小姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.35,0:15:44.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幹得漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.52,0:15:49.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個人 明明剛才還在這裡的…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.17,0:15:52.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是被同化了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.02,0:15:58.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是什麼玩意
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.71,0:16:01.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,地下還有誰活著？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.71,0:16:04.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,溝口先生正和醫療隊員一起往地面前進
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.66,0:16:08.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作為棄子足夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.87,0:16:18.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,溝口 請告知你現在的位置
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.19,0:16:20.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,地下六層
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.65,0:16:22.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可別把我們忘了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.57,0:16:24.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請立刻啟動地下的芬里爾
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.28,0:16:25.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是當真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.59,0:16:28.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真壁司令已經批准了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.44,0:16:32.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他以前倒是很沉著冷靜的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.56,0:16:34.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真不知道是誰教唆他的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.01,0:16:37.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要違抗司令的命令嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.28,0:16:40.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我照辦 我照辦總行了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.48,0:16:42.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快把啟動代碼告訴我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.66,0:17:00.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總士 找到芬里爾的啟動代碼了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.96,0:17:08.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是這樣 我有事要辦了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.48,0:17:09.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.56,0:17:17.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡果然也和我們那邊一樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.22,0:17:19.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 就是這個了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.56,0:17:22.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猜對了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.62,0:17:26.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把引爆時間設定在30分鐘後
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.11,0:17:30.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,30分鐘…也太快了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.82,0:17:32.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再長就危險了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.25,0:17:36.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,…明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.99,0:17:37.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,準備了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.26,0:17:40.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,3 2 1
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.63,0:17:45.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,芬里爾已啟動
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.56,0:17:49.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 撤退撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.58,0:18:01.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,芬里爾啟動了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.90,0:18:03.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們分頭行動
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.55,0:18:05.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一個人原地待命
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.98,0:18:07.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,另一個去搭救地下的人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.01,0:18:09.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要怎麼進入地下？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.46,0:18:10.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從海裡進去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.50,0:18:11.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.82,0:18:14.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們沒做到的事 由我來做！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.43,0:18:20.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 甲洋
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.91,0:18:23.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我命令你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.50,0:18:27.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你說往下走？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.33,0:18:29.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是唯一的逃脫路徑
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.42,0:18:32.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.17,0:18:35.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是不是強人所難了？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.37,0:18:39.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,應該說是值得聽從的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.62,0:18:41.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果海裡有敵人怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.10,0:18:42.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還是我去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.01,0:18:45.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是在對甲洋下命令
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.57,0:18:51.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有援軍 就你一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.78,0:18:54.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,話先說在前面
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.21,0:18:59.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像羽佐間那樣魯莽的行動我不會允許第二次
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.95,0:19:09.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果有損失法芙娜的風險
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.12,0:19:11.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就中止救援
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.36,0:19:20.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是說要看我的實力對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.40,0:19:23.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總士 起碼先確定一下海裡有沒有敵人！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.52,0:19:25.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們可沒在海裡戰鬥過啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.44,0:19:27.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是被襲擊了…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.93,0:19:30.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一騎 戰鬥是你的任務
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.35,0:19:35.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你去吸引島上敵人的注意力
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.65,0:19:58.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帶著這東西潛下去就行了是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.09,0:19:59.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.21,0:20:01.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,時限為10分鐘
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.51,0:20:10.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手 你們想讓法芙娜報銷嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.67,0:20:16.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真壁 真矢真的能回來…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.17,0:20:17.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.71,0:20:18.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.96,0:20:44.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要在這裡休息一下嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.24,0:20:47.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為沒武器了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.07,0:20:58.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也…我也能戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.38,0:21:13.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,消滅牠之後 其餘的敵人就會朝你衝過來 沒問題吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.76,0:21:14.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.36,0:21:18.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,馬上發動登陸艇
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.53,0:21:19.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 生還者…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.11,0:21:21.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是命令！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.37,0:21:56.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,開火！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.40,0:22:02.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們只是想要克服
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.16,0:22:07.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想要去做過去沒能做到的事
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.34,0:22:14.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一面告訴自己 這樣就能贖罪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.41,0:22:18.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一面沉入更幽深的黑暗
