Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.16,0:23:30.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凍結的心
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.31,0:23:34.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吶 春日井
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.68,0:23:36.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,醒一醒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.29,0:23:41.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下回 蒼穹的法芙娜 第九回
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.05,0:23:43.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同化 -生離-
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.53,0:23:48.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在那裡嗎
